INFO  2023-08-28 22:10:01,128 [1    ] oft.EntityFrameworkCore.Database.Command - Executed DbCommand (139ms) [Parameters=[@__language_Name_1='?' (Size = 128)], CommandType='Text', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT CASE
    WHEN EXISTS (
        SELECT 1
        FROM [Languages] AS [l]
        WHERE ([l].[TenantId] IS NULL) AND [l].[Name] = @__language_Name_1) THEN CAST(1 AS bit)
